only show these buyers

00:15:06.300 --> 00:15:10.420
your in-app purchase offers,
so that you can continue

00:15:10.420 --> 00:15:13.200
to monetize and keep them
retained in your app,

00:15:13.200 --> 00:15:14.960
while for the rest
of the users you can

00:15:14.960 --> 00:15:18.180
monetize through display ads.

00:15:18.180 --> 00:15:21.070
Another example of
AdMob is Mediation,

00:15:21.070 --> 00:15:24.460
which means you can run ads
across multiple ad networks

00:15:24.460 --> 00:15:26.760
