which of those is the highest

00:15:42.860 --> 00:15:45.030
paying, every ad request.

00:15:45.030 --> 00:15:46.830
And we only then
show the highest

00:15:46.830 --> 00:15:51.020
paying one in your app to help
you maximize your earnings.

00:15:51.020 --> 00:15:54.410
We're also investing
heavily into providing

00:15:54.410 --> 00:15:58.120
